{"tid":646390,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"李斯特城輸比水晶宮 5:0 熱刺最後一輪對李斯特城","createTime":"2018-04-29T04:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T08:05:31.000Z","uid":94771,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a8382f96ff0048621e79ada737cff4a4d0a13b","tid":646390,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T04:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知有無手足記得上年熱刺都係對李城<br />\n呢年最後一輪都係一樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/120158_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F120158_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=5cacb7d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重要係大炒李城6粒<br />\n而拎自己個女出來都要入波的哈利簡尼個場個人入左4粒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/120018_1c3a977bb7790c10bd8aa15b3eb07f44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F120018_1c3a977bb7790c10bd8aa15b3eb07f44.png&h=68ce1e9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙拉個神射手真係有機會無左<br />\n上年盧卡古個神射就係咁無左<br />\n<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7de47570b3933637db363daaed7ceaed8d53a5","tid":646390,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T04:21:43.000Z","msg":"今年冇態冇得刷咁多粒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de466251223e8c8488312d38ab191acde16e469","tid":646390,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1c7de47570b3933637db363daaed7ceaed8d53a5","tid":646390,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T04:21:43.000Z","msg":"今年冇態冇得刷咁多粒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"